```json
{
  "application": "PBS",
  "details": {
    "purpose": "Generation of scripts for running telemac simulations on a PBS system.",
    "features": [
      "Assigns a job name and number of processors.",
      "Defines a working directory.",
      "Counts the number of processors using the PBS_NODEFILE.",
      "Creates mpirun.txt and mpi_telemac.conf files for parallel execution.",
      "Starts the telemac code with specified parameters.",
      "Checks for running processes after completion."
    ],
    "requirements": [
      "PBS queue system",
      "Telemac software (codename)",
      "Bash shell"
    ],
    "input": [
      "jobname",
      "nbnodes (number of processors)",
      "codename",
      "casename"
    ],
    "output": "jobname.pbs script and Telemac simulation output files"
  }
}
```
